{
  "chapter": 29,
  "chapter_summary": "毛臬试图借仇独后人与金剑侠之名拖延局势，却被林琳揭露当年暗算仇独、害死程枫的旧恶，群雄离心。汪氏兄弟以两仪剑法合攻，丁衣也加入围攻，毛臬虽施灵蛇鞭法苦撑，终陷败局。毛文琪持琥珀神剑救父，逼退丁衣并使毛臬反杀汪一鹏，汪一鸣落水逃走，林琦琤和丁衣亦相继逃离。潘佥、程驹发现仇恕后离船，毛文琪揭穿船上还魂并非朱子明，又说明慕容惜生曾假扮还魂卧底。假还魂试剑脱身，掷出小金剑表明金剑侠身份。金超雄赶来宣布烧毁毛臬老巢，毛文琪劝父归隐，毛臬却在末路中大笑。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_peng",
      "text": "汪大弟，须知这次大会，乃为了对付仇独的后人而召开，当年之事，贤昆仲也有一份，怎地为了一时意气，而坏了大事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_peng",
      "speaker_name": "汪一鹏",
      "listener": "char_mao_nie",
      "text": "你狂傲跋扈，处心积虑地诛除异己，难道也是为了对付仇独的后人么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位可知道那仇独的后人，便是近日在江湖中，掀起无边风涛的'金剑侠'？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今日毛臬身受误会，死不足惜，但恐众家兄弟为此而各自生心，致力量分散，授人以各各击破之隙，咳咳……那时……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "灵蛇毛臬领袖草莽英雄垂十数年，江湖间总算平静无波，这次一旦将他的领导地位废掉，则后继之人能否有此魄力来担负这千钧重担？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "林琳",
      "listener": "char_mao_nie",
      "text": "当年是你用阴谋暗算仇独，使他两腿残废在先，你才是真正的罪魁祸首，仇独的儿子找的只有你！",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "林琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "诸位千万不要听他的，可怜程枫当年替他卖命，到头来反被他害死了！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_peng",
      "speaker_name": "汪一鹏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "程大哥夫妇的遭遇，便是咱们前车之鉴，今日不先杀了这不仁不义的恶贼，将来咱们便死无葬身之地了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "观战群雄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好剑法！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很好，毛臬倒要瞧瞧贤昆仲这'两仪剑法'，练到几成火候？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两仪剑法不过如此，咄！还不退下？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "毛臬且让贤昆仲展尽所学，然后才予以还击，好教你弟兄输得心服！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_peng",
      "speaker_name": "汪一鹏",
      "listener": "char_mao_nie",
      "text": "你想株守待援，简直做梦！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ming",
      "speaker_name": "汪一鸣",
      "listener": "char_mao_nie",
      "text": "放眼湖上，还有谁肯帮你这奸恶之人，你就乖乖认命罢。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群雄私语",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看样子毛大哥恐怕不行！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群雄私语",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到'河朔双剑'，竟这般厉害……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群雄私语",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们何不乘此时机，助他兄弟一臂，斗杀毛臬，拥立新盟主？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mao_nie",
      "text": "啊！爹爹！您真是这样的人吗？这众叛亲离的苦果，竟是您自己亲手种下的吗？啊！天呀！教我怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "汪氏昆仲与丁衣",
      "listener": "char_mao_nie",
      "text": "毛臬！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "汪氏昆仲与丁衣",
      "listener": "char_mao_nie",
      "text": "兄弟们如让你的长鞭再攻得三招，便将三颗人头奉送！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_ding_yi",
      "text": "撒手！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": "char_wang_yi_peng",
      "text": "去！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你两人还有什么话说？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "林琦琤",
      "listener": "char_mao_nie",
      "text": "毛大哥，方才可没有我的事，您怎么把账算到我头上，若不是文琪世妹赶来，我也会帮毛大哥出手的！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "林琦琤",
      "listener": "char_mao_nie",
      "text": "毛大哥，我将他交给你，我要走了！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pan_qian",
      "speaker_name": "潘佥",
      "listener": "char_cheng_ju",
      "text": "你看到恕儿了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_ju",
      "speaker_name": "程驹",
      "listener": "char_pan_qian",
      "text": "早就看到了，他正躲躲藏藏地站在那边堤岸上，却躲不开我的眼光，只是他既不愿现身，我们也最好不要多事出手！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pan_qian",
      "speaker_name": "潘佥",
      "listener": "char_cheng_ju",
      "text": "我们既然看到了他，还在这里做什么？走吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位哪里去？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mao_nie",
      "text": "爹爹，不要追了，追也追不到的，这船上还有个更可恨的人，你老人家难道还不知道么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mao_nie",
      "text": "你老人家难道以为他真的是闪电神刀朱子明么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "他不是朱子明是什么人？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mao_nie",
      "text": "朱子明早已死了，他只不过是借着朱子明的名义，假扮成'还魂'后神智不清的样子，来骗你老人家的，而且他还不是第一个'还魂'！第一个'还魂'，是我师姐！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "你师姐……第一个'还魂'……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mao_nie",
      "text": "这件事说来话长，我一时说不清楚……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_jia_huan_hun",
      "text": "但你若是英雄，就请将你的真面目现出来，堂堂的男子汉，藏头露尾，隐姓埋名，莫非连女子都不如？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_jia_huan_hun",
      "text": "你笑什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_huan_hun",
      "speaker_name": "还魂",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "不错！我假冒'还魂'是为了要骗你爹爹，但我却也未曾想到，那第一个'还魂'竟然也是假冒的，我一生之中，从未遇到这样曲折离奇，这样令人糊涂的事，只要你将此事真相说出，我一定也将真面目现出！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_jia_huan_hun",
      "text": "你说话算不算数？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_huan_hun",
      "speaker_name": "还魂",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "君子一言，快马一鞭。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_jia_huan_hun",
      "text": "我师姐慕容惜生，为了要探查那仇独之子的真相，是以假冒成早已死了的闪电神刀朱子明，卧底在仇独之子家里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_huan_hun",
      "speaker_name": "还魂",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "她为了乔装易容，所以才扮成这种样子，而我却以为世上真有其人，不想却上了她的当！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_jia_huan_hun",
      "text": "我师姐天纵奇才，你怎么比得上她！你只想帮仇独儿子的忙，又见到'还魂'的形状，易容乔装，便背了程枫的尸身，到我家来卧底，其实那程枫也是仇独之子杀死的",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "到底谁是那仇独的儿子，他此刻在哪里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_jia_huan_hun",
      "text": "我已将此事的真相说出，你呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_huan_hun",
      "speaker_name": "还魂",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "你定要知道我是谁么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_jia_huan_hun",
      "text": "你若不愿自动说出，只怕我这柄剑也容不得你的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_huan_hun",
      "speaker_name": "还魂",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "无论我是否自动说出，你这柄剑我也要领教领教的！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_jia_huan_hun",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_jia_huan_hun",
      "text": "你到底是{十么人？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_jian_xia",
      "speaker_name": "金剑侠",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "你要知道我是谁么？看看这个！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金剑侠！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "想不到金剑侠这厮竟在我的船上！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mao_nie",
      "text": "爹爹，你老人家……你老人家……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "毛臬一生闯荡江湖，成败且不论它，终算能交着各位这几位朋友，毛臬已是十分……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_chao_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "金超雄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若非毛臬之友，快离湖船，以免自误！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": "char_jin_chao_xiong",
      "text": "金超雄，你也来了！",
